Title : Firvale
Text : :''This article is for the community in British Columbia, Canada.  For the school in England, see [[Fir Vale School]].''
'''Firvale''' is a community in the [[Bella Coola, British Columbia|Bella Coola Valley]] of the [[British Columbia Coast|Central Coast region]] of [[British Columbia]], Canada, located at the confluence of [[Burnt Bridge Creek (British Columbia)|Burnt Bridge Creek]] and the [[Bella Coola River]], northeast of the valley's main community of Bella Coola.<ref>[http://apps.gov.bc.ca/pub/bcgnws/names/12776.html BC Names/GeoBC entry "Firvale (community)"]</ref>

